{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01YC2Ky6nHLc3qWzdzfAt1gv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete understanding of the codebase. This is a Quarkus + JSF (MyFaces) address book application with JPA/Hibernate. The migration strategy will be:\n\n**Quarkus + JSF + CDI + JPA** -> **Spring Boot + Spring MVC (REST API) + Spring Data JPA + Thymeleaf (for views)**\n\nSince JSF doesn't have a direct Spring Boot equivalent, I'll convert the JSF-based CRUD to Spring MVC REST controllers with Thymeleaf templates, preserving all business logic.\n\nLet me update the todo list and start the migration."}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":10078,"cache_read_input_tokens":36861,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":10078,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":655},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fd257968-fc09-4865-84ad-86d17cc4ff85","uuid":"c6e7ee0a-2085-4606-8a20-79b8db775b72"}
